Shout out to Python.plainenglish.io for basic login and registration structure! 
ref: https://python.plainenglish.io/user-registration-and-login-authentication-in-django-2f3450479409


Running the app locally:

to run the project: docker-compose up

in case of error please try: docker-compose run web python manage.py makemigrations users
then: docker-compose run web python manage.py migrate
and docker-compose up again


Once running go to:

http://localhost:80 